item.description:
The first step is to screw the ONT into the wall in a convenient place using drywall achors. The ONT we are currently using is the Ubiquiti &ldquo;UFiber loco GPON CPE&rdquo;
Only use white fiber inside apartments, never yellow or any other color. This is to better blend in with the wall. We have custom made 3mm white fiber with termination at one end.
Once the ONT is screwed into the wall, plug in the terminated end of the white fiber.
